Obtiene el template CSV con headers y ejemplo.

## Response
```json
{
  "template": "email,display_name,first_name,...",
  "example": "player@example.com,John Doe,John,...",
  "fields": {
    "email": {
      "required": true,
      "description": "Player email address"
    },
    ...
  }
}
```

